2i5ev"><div class="css-1ne9mcl"><div class="css-1fvp4bv"></div><div><p class="css-4kagyz">Current Version</p></div></div></div><div class="css-128knw7"><div class="css-1vm0jh3"><div class="css-r2ciw3"></div><div><p class="css-4kagyz">May 7, 2021</p><div><p class="css-jzq737">Edited By</p><p class="css-g9w29o">Afton DeLucca</p></div><div><p class="css-jzq737">Medically Reviewed By</p><p class="css-g9w29o">Susan Bard, MD</p></div><div><p class="css-jzq737">Copy Edited By</p><p class="css-g9w29o">Chris Doka</p></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div data-testid="share-tools" class="css-j9nycp"><p>Share this article</p><div class="css-1svc4lv"><div class="button-wrapper print"><a class="css-98pbp3 print button icon icon-hl-print" target="_blank" title="Print this page"></a></div><div class="button-wrapper email"><a class="css-98pbp3 email button icon icon-hl-email" target="_blank" title="Email this page"></a></div><div class="button-wrapper facebook"><a class="css-98pbp3 facebook button icon icon-hl-facebook" href="https://www.facebook.com/sharer/sharer.php?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.healthline.com%2Fhealth%2Fskin-lumps%2Flipoma-treatment-in-ayurveda%3Futm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_campaign%3Dsocial-sharebar-referred-desktop" rel="noopener noreferrer nofollow" target="_blank" title="Share on Facebook"></a></div><div class="button-wrapper twitter"><a class="css-98pbp3 twitter button icon icon-hl-twitter" href="https://twitter.com/intent/tweet?via=healthline&amp;text=Ayurvedic%20Treatment%20for%20Lipomas&amp;url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.healthline.com%2Fhealth%2Fskin-lumps%2Flipoma-treatment-in-ayurveda%3Futm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dtwitter%26utm_campaign%3Dsocial-sharebar-referred-desktop" rel="noopener noreferrer nofollow" target="_blank" title="Share on Twitter"></a></div><div class="button-wrapper more"><a class="css-98pbp3 more button icon icon-hl-more" target="_blank" title="Show more"></a></div></div></div></div></div><span class="css-zya5